    "There are two attacks on complete HIGHT [56,57].",
    "KASUMI: KASUMI is specially designed to fulfill security requirements for the mobile network, which includes GSM, EDGE, UMTS, and GPRS.",
    "KASUMI supports 3GPP confidentiality and the 3GPP integrity algorithm.",
